      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli[es]</strong> finely into rounds (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Zest your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, and cut in half</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2tsp]</span> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a small bowl with the juice of <strong>half </strong>the <strong>lime[s] </strong>and the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>and set aside<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>quick-pickled chilli</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1679659650272-x200.jpg",
