          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> to a bowl with<strong> half</strong> the <strong>coconut marinade</strong> (you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>sunshine mayo</strong></p>",
