        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coconut marinated chicken</strong> and cook for 6 min on each side or until slightly charred and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spicy coconut chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
