    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>gluten</strong> <strong>free</strong> <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
