            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed brioche </strong>with a handful of <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>,<strong> </strong>the<strong> spicy coconut chicken</strong>,<strong> </strong>a dollop of<strong> sunshine mayo </strong>and<strong> </strong>the<strong> quick-pickled chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), reserve the<strong> pickling liquid</strong> from the pickled chilli</p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining baby leaf salad </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and the <strong>reserved pickling liquid</strong> and<strong> </strong>set the<strong> fries </strong>and any <strong>remaining sunshine mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
